      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Grid convergence index — mesh independence study",
      "description": "Three-level mesh refinement study on FDA pump geometry. Coarse (4.2M cells), medium (11.8M cells), fine (28.5M cells). GCI for hemolysis index: 1.7% (fine-to-medium), 4.1% (medium-to-coarse). Fine mesh selected for production runs.",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/evidence/ev-01-mesh-refinement-study",
      "wasAttributedTo": "https://uofa.net/synth/org/morrison-cfd-lab"
    },
