      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison — FDA pump benchmark",
      "description": "Particle image velocimetry measurements from FDA benchmark dataset compared against CFD velocity fields at three axial planes. Mean absolute error in axial velocity: 4.3% of bulk velocity. Turbulent kinetic energy agreement within 18% in impeller passage. Validation metric: E_rms = 0.031 m/s.",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/evidence/ev-02-fda-piv-benchmark-data",
      "wasAttributedTo": "https://uofa.net/synth/org/fda-cdrh-benchmark-program"
