      "description": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against 12 bench measurements spanning the VAD operating envelope. Pearson r = 0.91. Mean bias: +0.06 g/dL/100 mL (overprediction, conservative). 95% prediction interval encompasses all experimental observations.",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/evidence/ev-03-hemolysis-bench-experiments",
      "wasAttributedTo": "https://uofa.net/synth/org/morrison-cfd-lab"
