      "rationale": "E_rms and mean bias computed for NIH across 12 bench points. Pearson r = 0.91. Formal statistical equivalence test not performed; equivalence bounds not pre-specified. Prediction intervals reported but not formally calibrated. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
