      "rationale": "NIH is the primary regulatory QoI and matches the validation metric. However, spatial averaging domain differs: CFD integrates over full fluid volume while bench measurement samples outlet port only. Temporal averaging window for pulsatile cases not harmonized. Achieved level 3."
