      "rationale": "Hemolysis coefficients taken from literature (Giersiepen 1990); no independent calibration performed. Coefficient uncertainty estimated as ±20% uniform distribution without statistical justification. Inlet waveform uncertainty characterized from 5 patient measurements — insufficient for MRL 5 requirement of population-representative characterization. Achieved level 2."
